belongs here in this office... 

2214
02:17:59,280 --> 02:18:01,160
... and I accept that. 

2215
02:18:01,200 --> 02:18:04,560
There can be no whitewash
At the White House. 

2216
02:18:04,640 --> 02:18:06,960
Two wrongs
do not make a right. 

2217
02:18:07,040 --> 02:18:08,840
Now, I love America. 

2218
02:18:08,880 --> 02:18:13,320
God bless America,
and God bless each and every one of you. 

2219
02:18:14,800 --> 02:18:17,880
And we're clear. 

2220
02:18:20,360 --> 02:18:22,360
Out. 

2221
02:18:40,120 --> 02:18:42,000
Thank you. 

2222
02:18:47,760 --> 02:18:50,120
Are you going
to Key Biscayne?

2223
